Package: EventStudy
Type: Package
Title: Event Study Analysis
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2026-02-20
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Simon",
           family = "Mueller",
           role = c("cre", "aut"),
           email = "sm@data-zoo.de"))
Maintainer: Simon Mueller <sm@data-zoo.de>
Description: Perform financial event study analysis in R. Implements the
    classical event study methodology (MacKinlay 1997) with multiple return
    models (Market Model, Market Adjusted, Comparison Period Mean Adjusted),
    parametric and non-parametric test statistics, and visualization tools.
URL: https://github.com/sipemu/eventstudy
BugReports: https://github.com/sipemu/eventstudy/issues
License: AGPL-3
